qvqFDdx7mMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">有用户由此推测为什么 Anthropic 没有收购 OpenClaw，因为他们也早就想这么做了，而且做得更好。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3685185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503795865\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8abb9c3b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNjnR7t35LroibjjMCZLDdESkEyPSALYdvcplDYlORW1PQicjvZzroNmM7fzlLRypWbxmOMEbLO9Vw28adaR0rHuGCY2vRnpysWtw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e73ec7e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNgdREiaR5icJSUQMESicLmkLVqtoibOCU2UoNUy5UTHY4Tia2S1ibAsZbwibHePqIHedcNtIebmCXCRCePrFzozSRkU8AcvRQiaSUmlpVo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></span><span leaf=\"\">OpenClaw 同日升级，底层架构“大换血” </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">没错，Claude 此次的更新和这阵子爆火的 OpenClaw 干的活儿有异曲同工之处。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而就在 Anthropic 发布 Claude“计算机使用能力”的同一时间窗口，已经加入 OpenAI 的 OpenClaw 创始人对外披露，OpenClaw 也迎来重大更新，不仅提升了大脑（模型）的智商，还彻底翻新了它的手脚（插件系统）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对插件系统的重构是本次更新最亮眼的地方</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。OpenClaw 将以前的旧插件接口（扩展 API）停用了，并新上线了全新的官方插件开发工具包（SDK）。开发者可以写出的功能会更稳定，运行更顺畅。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方还明确了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">ClawHub</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;将是以后下载、安装插件的首选。就像手机的 App Store 一样，这能保证用户安装的插件是干净、安全、没有广告或病毒的，整个生态环境更纯净。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，针对 Windows 系统还增加了专门的拦截机制，加固了软件运行的环境。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9287037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503795864\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d28365ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNiaQacwcmLkB5SZvPr4EWB3pR8zibsia5PKMqY798Wdmf5xKuDosOc5sg9nLNMFicgokqia5WBeEaoEmtg5gldtcibiaEBDvp52Pichl3c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了插件系统外，OpenClaw 的“大脑”——模型也升级到了 M 2.7、GPT-5.4。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 UI 上也有更新，包括长对话压缩机制、安卓端深色模式、多平台通知功能等都进行了精细打磨。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">此次更新向外界释放了一个明确信号：OpenClaw 要开启“生态通吃”的兼容性进化，3.22 版本正式打通了与 Claude、Codex 以及 Cursor 三大顶流开发工具的边界。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过自动映射机制，这些外部工具的插件包（Skills）可以无缝接入 OpenClaw 的技能体系。这意味着，那些你在 Cursor 里用得顺手的顶级插件，现在可以“一键迁移”到 OpenClaw 中跑起来。从一个深耕自研的封闭框架，转变为一个吸纳全球开发者红利的开放平台，OpenClaw 这一步走得既狠又准。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论如何，两个顶级 Agent 项目同一日发布更新，对于开发者来言总是利好的，这意味着大家有更多更好的选择。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">从目前的发展来看，无论是 OpenClaw 所代表的“系统化 Agent 路线”，还是 Claude 这次选择的“直接操控电脑”路径，本质上都在逼近同一个目标：让 AI 真正替人完成工作，而不仅仅是提供建议。前者强调结构化、可扩展和长周期任务执行能力，更像是在搭建一套“AI 操作系统”；后者则通过模拟人类操作，降低使用门槛，把执行能力快速带到真实应用场景中，更接近“即插即用的数字员工”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">两种路径各有优势，也各有尚未解决的难题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">问题也随之变得直接——如果是你，会更倾向于 Claude 还是 OpenClaw？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 AI 开始真正接管工作的时代，用户的选择，或许也会反过来决定这场路线之争的最终走向。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4492753623188406\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"width: 444px;height: 643px;\" data-imgfileid=\"503795863\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e82fbdb2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNhzccFcWNGzwDtto7BNcicsXsN4ian2RBeYEp7xFyaAzVzTe2td5kW3jYXsMDrLBYKwYJOwf1VFicgnNrYDib3rIyFib0fvBwGgHGtc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p class=\"mp_vote_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-vote class=\"js_editor_vote_card js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_vote_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvote\" data-supervoteid=\"463050981\" data-expiretime=\"0\" data-votesubject=\"[{&quot;type&quot;:1,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;你会更倾向于 Claude 还是 OpenClaw？ &quot;,&quot;options&quot;:[{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Claude&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0},{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;OpenClaw&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0},{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;两个都会用&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0}],&quot;total_cnt&quot;:0}]\" data-delflag=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\"></mp-common-vote></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">参考链接：</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://claude.com/product/cowork#dispatch-and-computer-use\" target=\"_blank\">https://claude.com/product/cowork#dispatch-and-computer-use</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://x.com/claudeai/status/2036195789601374705\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/claudeai/status/2036195789601374705</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/releases/tag/v2026.3.22-beta.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/releases/tag/v2026.3.22-beta.1</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">‍<a href=\"https://www.engadget.com/ai/claude-code-and-cowork-can-now-use-your-computer-210000126.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.engadget.com/ai/claude-code-and-cowork-can-now-use-your-computer-210000126.html</a></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Anthropic 发布 Claude Code 重大更新，支持 AI 直接操控电脑屏幕、鼠标和键盘，与 OpenAI 旗下的 OpenClaw 展开 Agent 赛道正面竞争。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Anthropic 发布 Claude Code 重大更新，支持 AI 直接操控电脑屏幕、鼠标和键盘，与 OpenAI 旗下的 OpenClaw 展开 Agent 赛道正面竞争。",
  "summary": "本文详细报道了 Anthropic 对 Claude Code 与 Claude Cowork 的里程碑式升级，其核心在于 AI 具备了直接“操控电脑”的能力，能够模拟人类进行点击、滚动和导航，而不再局限于 API 调用。文章介绍了该功能的运行机制、安全防护措施以及新增的 Dispatch 跨设备协作功能。同时，文章对比了同日更新的 OpenClaw（已加入 OpenAI 阵营），后者通过重构插件系统 SDK 和升级至 GPT-5.4 模型强化其系统化 Agent 路线。两者的竞争标志着 AI 正在从“对话助手”向具备独立执行能力的“数字操作员”转变。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Claude 实现“电脑操控”能力，AI 可直接模拟人类操作屏幕、鼠标和键盘。",
      "explanation": "AI 不再依赖预设的 API 接口，而是通过视觉识别和模拟输入直接控制操作系统，能够处理没有插件支持的复杂交互任务。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Anthropic 推出 Dispatch 功能，实现跨设备的持续任务管理。",
      "explanation": "用户可以通过手机发起指令，让 Claude 在远程电脑端执行如邮件检查、代码运行、PR 提交等自动化工作流。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OpenClaw 重构插件系统并升级模型，走系统化 Agent 路线。",
      "explanation": "OpenClaw 3.22 版本通过全新 SDK 和 ClawHub 强化生态安全性，并实现了与 Claude、Cursor 插件体系的无缝兼容。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 竞争焦点从“生成”转向“执行”，重塑人机交互关系。",
      "explanation": "行业共识正从聊天机器人转向“实用型 AI”，即能够理解模糊指令并独立在复杂软件环境中完成闭环任务的执行主体。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 不再只是调用工具，而是可以直接「操控你的电脑」。",
    "这不再只是一个聊天机器人，而是开始具备「干活能力」的系统。",
    "AI 的角色将发生根本转变——从辅助工具，转向可以独立完成任务的执行主体。",
    "前者强调结构化、可扩展和长周期任务执行能力，更像是在搭建一套「AI 操作系统」；后者则通过模拟人类操作，降低使用门槛。"
  ],
